0: SELECT DISTINCT      IAP_SUBJECT_DETAIL.ACTIVITY_TITLE,      IAP_SUBJECT_SESSION.SESSION_LOCATION,      ACADEMIC_TERMS_ALL.TERM_START_DATE,      IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON.PERSON_NAME FROM      IAP_SUBJECT_DETAIL JOIN      IAP_SUBJECT_SESSION ON IAP_SUBJECT_DETAIL.IAP_SUBJECT_SESSION_KEY = IAP_SUBJECT_SESSION.IAP_SUBJECT_SESSION_KEY JOIN      ACADEMIC_TERMS_ALL ON IAP_SUBJECT_DETAIL.TERM_CODE = ACADEMIC_TERMS_ALL.TERM_CODE JOIN      IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON ON IAP_SUBJECT_DETAIL.IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON_KEY = IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON.IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON_KEY WHERE      IAP_SUBJECT_PERSON.PERSON_ROLE = 'Activity leader' ORDER BY      ACADEMIC_TERMS_ALL.TERM_START_DATE ASC;	----- bird -----	dw
1: SELECT DISTINCT      FR.ROOM_FULL_NAME,      B.BUILDING_NAME,      B.BUILDING_STREET_ADDRESS,      FBA.CITY,      FBA.STATE,      FBA.POSTAL_CODE,      FB.BUILDING_HEIGHT FROM      FCLT_ROOMS FR JOIN      COURSE_CATALOG_SUBJECT_OFFERED CCSO ON CCSO.MEET_PLACE = FR.FCLT_ROOM_KEY JOIN      FCLT_BUILDING_ADDRESS FBA ON FBA.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY = FR.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY JOIN      FCLT_BUILDING FB ON FB.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY = FR.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY JOIN      BUILDINGS B ON B.BUILDING_KEY = FR.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY WHERE      CCSO.DEPARTMENT_NAME = 'Electrical Eng & Computer Sci';	----- bird -----	dw
2: SELECT      FCLT_BUILDING.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY AS building_key,     FCLT_BUILDING.BUILDING_NAME AS building_name,     COUNT(DISTINCT CIS_COURSE_CATALOG.SUBJECT_ID) AS number_of_courses FROM      CIS_COURSE_CATALOG JOIN      COURSE_CATALOG_SUBJECT_OFFERED ON CIS_COURSE_CATALOG.SUBJECT_ID = COURSE_CATALOG_SUBJECT_OFFERED.SUBJECT_ID JOIN      FCLT_ROOMS ON COURSE_CATALOG_SUBJECT_OFFERED.MEET_PLACE = FCLT_ROOMS.FCLT_ROOM_KEY JOIN      FCLT_BUILDING ON FCLT_ROOMS.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY = FCLT_BUILDING.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY GROUP BY      FCLT_BUILDING.FCLT_BUILDING_KEY, FCLT_BUILDING.BUILDING_NAME;	----- bird -----	dw
3: SELECT b.BUILDING_NAME, f.FLOOR FROM FAC_BUILDING b JOIN FAC_FLOOR f ON b.FAC_BUILDING_KEY = f.BUILDING_KEY ORDER BY CAST(f.FLOOR AS UNSIGNED) DESC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	dw
4: SELECT      COUNT(DISTINCT ml.MOIRA_LIST_NAME) AS mailing_list_count,     ml.MOIRA_LIST_NAME AS list_with_max_members,     COUNT(mld.MOIRA_LIST_MEMBER) AS max_member_count FROM      MOIRA_LIST ml JOIN      MOIRA_LIST_DETAIL mld ON ml.MOIRA_LIST_KEY = mld.MOIRA_LIST_KEY JOIN      SE_PERSON sp ON mld.MOIRA_LIST_MEMBER = sp.KRB_NAME WHERE      ml.MOIRA_LIST_NAME LIKE 'B%'      AND sp.ORGANIZATION = 'Electrical Engineering-Computer Science' GROUP BY      ml.MOIRA_LIST_NAME ORDER BY      max_member_count DESC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	dw
5: SELECT      c.SUBJECT_TITLE,     COUNT(DISTINCT e.FULL_NAME) AS number_of_instructors,     MAX(CHAR_LENGTH(e.FULL_NAME)) AS longest_instructor_name_length FROM      COURSE_CATALOG_SUBJECT_OFFERED c JOIN      EMPLOYEE_DIRECTORY e ON c.RESPONSIBLE_FACULTY_MIT_ID = e.MIT_ID JOIN      ACADEMIC_TERMS_ALL a ON c.TERM_CODE = a.TERM_CODE WHERE      c.IS_OFFERED_SUMMER_TERM = 'Y' GROUP BY      c.SUBJECT_TITLE;	----- bird -----	dw
